            "stanza_text": "Jadis Mangin, froid, sous son casque,\nCrossait les badauds de Paris ;\nJ'aimais son boniment fantasque,\nJ'aimais l'orgue de Vert-de-Gris."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "J'aime à Notre-Dame, en carême,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Un prédicateur virulent ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Certes, son orgue est plus ronflant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mais son boniment, c'est le même !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J'aime à Notre-Dame, en carême,\nUn prédicateur virulent ;\nCertes, son orgue est plus ronflant,\nMais son boniment, c'est le même !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "«Pêcheurs, achetez nos pardons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "»La sainte Église attend vos dons ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "»Soyez fervents, soyez dociles !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "«Pêcheurs, achetez nos pardons,\n»La sainte Église attend vos dons ;\n»Soyez fervents, soyez dociles !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "»Et, confits dans ces vérités,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "g"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "»O mes frères qui m'écoutez,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "g"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Allez en paix ! — Tas d'imbéciles !»",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "»Et, confits dans ces vérités,\n»O mes frères qui m'écoutez,\nAllez en paix ! — Tas d'imbéciles !»"
        }
